389
00:28:16,488 --> 00:28:17,960
(Only a fool doesn't want
to make money (256))

390
00:28:17,963 --> 00:28:18,883
Guys,

391
00:28:19,403 --> 00:28:21,203
I've been idle recently.

392
00:28:21,602 --> 00:28:24,082
Does anyone have any jobs
that I can take on?

393
00:28:24,683 --> 00:28:25,362
Thanks.

394
00:28:33,440 --> 00:28:35,280
(Why is Mr. Yu begging for work
everywhere lately?)

395
00:28:35,280 --> 00:28:38,153
(We landed the post-production
for "Love Reality Show" Season 2)

396
00:28:38,153 --> 00:28:41,014
(The pay is decent, but no one
has taken the rough cut yet.)

397
00:28:41,014 --> 00:28:42,750
(Interested?)

398
00:28:43,282 --> 00:28:44,403
I'll take it!

399
00:28:47,723 --> 00:28:48,883
Also, guys,

400
00:28:49,243 --> 00:28:51,562
I can take on multiple projects
at the same time,

401
00:28:51,762 --> 00:28:53,443
and I guarantee quality.

402
00:28:54,282 --> 00:28:55,483
If anyone else has work,

403
00:28:55,483 --> 00:28:56,723
feel free to pass it my way too.

404
00:28:56,842 --> 00:28:57,802
Thanks.

405
00:29:06,040 --> 00:29:08,720
(How to Take Care of Your Girlfriend
and Make Her Feel Loved)

406
00:29:09,673 --> 00:29:11,137
(24 Ways to Take Care
of Your Girlfriend)

407
00:29:11,138 --> 00:29:12,600
(Never Compare Her
to Your Ex-Girlfriend)

408
00:29:17,767 --> 00:29:19,346
(Call: Guan Xingxin)

409
00:29:19,360 --> 00:29:20,640
(Guan Xingxin - Dialing)

410
00:29:22,203 --> 00:29:22,883
Sorry.

411
00:29:23,403 --> 00:29:25,963
The number you have dialed
is currently unavailable.

412
00:29:27,920 --> 00:29:31,320
(Yu Dule, Guan Xingxin, Smiling Gu Yi)

413
00:29:31,320 --> 00:29:33,320
(Yu Dule - Dialing)

414
00:29:56,480 --> 00:29:59,560
(Player's Guidebook)

415
00:30:08,802 --> 00:30:09,963
Welcome.

416
00:30:11,042 --> 00:30:12,082
Safe travels.

417
00:30:16,963 --> 00:30:17,963
Did you ask to see me?

418
00:30:18,562 --> 00:30:19,082
Yes.

419
00:30:20,003 --> 00:30:20,842
I want to talk to you.

420
00:30:23,082 --> 00:30:24,762
We're not that close yet.

421
00:30:25,602 --> 00:30:26,483
It's something important.

422
00:30:27,304 --> 00:30:29,160
If it's okay with you,
can we talk somewhere else?

423
00:30:30,082 --> 00:30:31,282
I don't want Gu Yi to know.

424
00:30:33,723 --> 00:30:34,443
Welcome.

425
00:30:34,683 --> 00:30:35,163
Let's go.

426
00:30:36,723 --> 00:30:37,562
Welcome.

427
00:30:47,003 --> 00:30:47,762
Hop on.

428
00:30:49,522 --> 00:30:50,643
On that?

429
00:30:51,320 --> 00:30:52,600
I'm not used to that type of ride.

430
00:30:54,963 --> 00:30:55,643
Are we going or not?

431
00:31:14,968 --> 00:31:15,720
What are you doing?

432
00:31:15,963 --> 00:31:16,802
Looking for the seat belt?

433
00:31:18,522 --> 00:31:19,443
Where should I grab?

434
00:31:20,842 --> 00:31:21,562
Anywhere.

435
00:31:22,403 --> 00:31:23,322
Just don't touch me.

436
00:32:24,163 --> 00:32:24,802
Liang Daiwen.

437
00:32:25,243 --> 00:32:26,199
Aren't you embarrassed

438
00:32:26,200 --> 00:32:27,208
holding on to me like that?

439
00:32:28,602 --> 00:32:29,082
Let go!

440
00:32:31,203 --> 00:32:32,362
How could I not hold onto you?

441
00:32:33,403 --> 00:32:35,322
You nearly hit the Earth's
escape velocity.

442
00:32:35,723 --> 00:32:36,762
If we crash,

443
00:32:37,443 --> 00:32:39,602
at least I'll die

444
00:32:40,483 --> 00:32:41,403
with dignity.

445
00:32:45,080 --> 00:32:46,440
Have you had enough of speeding?

446
00:32:47,362 --> 00:32:47,963
I have.

447
00:32:49,483 --> 00:32:50,483
Let's find a place to sit

448
00:32:51,522 --> 00:32:51,963
and talk.

449
00:32:59,522 --> 00:33:00,683
Here's your dessert.

450
00:33:01,842 --> 00:33:02,483
And your bill.

451
00:33:05,683 --> 00:33:06,282
That's it?

452
00:33:08,122 --> 00:33:08,963
Why is there only one?

453
00:33:12,643 --> 00:33:13,483
The waiter said

454
00:33:14,008 --> 00:33:14,840
it was enough for two.

455
00:33:20,762 --> 00:33:21,762
You're so stingy.

456
00:33:31,163 --> 00:33:31,923
Alright, alright.

457
00:33:32,122 --> 00:33:33,203
Say what you need to say.

458
00:33:34,042 --> 00:33:36,443
This isn't exactly the best place
for two men to hang out.

459
00:33:44,522 --> 00:33:45,362
Teach me

460
00:33:46,122 --> 00:33:47,322
how to take care of Gu Yi.

461
00:33:51,602 --> 00:33:52,362
Liang Daiwen,

462
00:33:53,203 --> 00:33:55,322
if you even remotely
considered me a rival,

463
00:33:55,522 --> 00:33:57,042
you wouldn't be asking me this, right?

464
00:33:58,243 --> 00:33:59,282
What are you thinking?

465
00:34:01,562 --> 00:34:02,483
I don't have many options.

466
00:34:03,122 --> 00:34:03,963
You know Gu Yi.

467
00:34:05,122 --> 00:34:05,923
Besides,

468
00:34:08,403 --> 00:34:09,763
when I wasn't around,

469
00:34:10,392 --> 00:34:11,688
you were the one taking care of her.

470
00:34:14,162 --> 00:34:15,843
Then ask your friends.

471
00:34:16,483 --> 00:34:17,082
I did.

472
00:34:18,963 --> 00:34:19,883
One's unreachable.

473
00:34:20,803 --> 00:34:21,283
The other

474
00:34:21,544 --> 00:34:22,424
is staying elsewhere.

475
00:34:23,432 --> 00:34:24,888
Another just wants to mess with me.

476
00:34:29,483 --> 00:34:30,803
So how do you usually

477
00:34:31,242 --> 00:34:32,283
get along with people?

478
00:34:33,363 --> 00:34:34,602
I've watched a lot of TV dramas.

479
00:34:36,403 --> 00:34:36,963
But

480
00:34:39,403 --> 00:34:41,363
Gu Yi doesn't like it
when I imitate TV dramas.

481
00:34:45,963 --> 00:34:47,363
You can't manage a relationship

482
00:34:48,280 --> 00:34:49,480
without imitating TV dramas?

483
00:34:55,242 --> 00:34:56,323
Not just a relationship.

484
00:34:57,803 --> 00:34:59,162
I want to become her family.

485
00:35:00,242 --> 00:35:00,963
To make her feel

486
00:35:01,722 --> 00:35:03,162
that she can always rely on me.

487
00:35:05,242 --> 00:35:05,722
Wait...

488
00:35:07,082 --> 00:35:07,923
Did something happen

489
00:35:08,003 --> 00:35:08,923
to Gu Yi's family?

490
00:35:16,242 --> 00:35:18,082
If you want to become her family,

491
00:35:19,202 --> 00:35:20,323
you need to make a statement.

492
00:35:26,763 --> 00:35:28,483
Even though I don't want to help you,

493
00:35:29,803 --> 00:35:32,443
I've seen Gu Yi having mood swings

494
00:35:33,082 --> 00:35:34,082
because of you too many times.

495
00:35:35,202 --> 00:35:36,682
She's indecisive in love.

496
00:35:37,003 --> 00:35:38,122
She really feels insecure.

497
00:35:40,162 --> 00:35:41,602
If you want to become her family,

498
00:35:42,923 --> 00:35:43,642
first of all,

499
00:35:43,803 --> 00:35:45,443
she needs to believe
you've got the commitment.

500
00:35:50,483 --> 00:35:51,042
Commitment?

501
00:35:53,722 --> 00:35:55,403
The commitment to give her a home.

502
00:36:17,483 --> 00:36:18,363
Commitment.

503
00:37:51,082 --> 00:37:52,242
That's

504
00:37:52,923 --> 00:37:54,242
a cat and a robot.

505
00:37:56,082 --> 00:37:57,042
It's you and me.

506
00:37:58,082 --> 00:37:59,323
Your bed is too low.

507
00:38:00,042 --> 00:38:01,242
No matter how hard I tried,

508
00:38:01,443 --> 00:38:02,682
I couldn't stick it under the bed.

509
00:38:03,528 --> 00:38:05,080
So we can only look at it
while lying down.

510
00:38:11,803 --> 00:38:13,363
There's something I want to tell you.

511
00:38:17,803 --> 00:38:19,963
After the last magazine interview
was published,

512
00:38:20,963 --> 00:38:22,722
we got several project proposals.

513
00:38:23,642 --> 00:38:24,722
Li Ai said thank you.

514
00:38:30,403 --> 00:38:31,682
As for Mr. Lu's Fluffy Theater,

515
00:38:32,483 --> 00:38:33,283
I've subleased it.

516
00:38:34,483 --> 00:38:35,042
In the future,

517
00:38:36,042 --> 00:38:37,283
there will occasionally be

518
00:38:37,283 --> 00:38:38,642
accessibility design salons.

519
00:38:39,202 --> 00:38:41,283
If you want to do a real
stand-up comedy theater,

520
00:38:42,042 --> 00:38:43,522
I'll apply for the performance license.

521
00:38:44,682 --> 00:38:45,682
Let's work hard together.

522
00:38:46,642 --> 00:38:47,883
No one should give up on their dreams.

523
00:38:58,763 --> 00:38:59,483
I know.

524
00:39:02,242 --> 00:39:03,722
I still haven't developed enough.

525
00:39:05,483 --> 00:39:06,042
I'm clingy,

526
00:39:07,443 --> 00:39:08,162
slow to react

527
00:39:09,642 --> 00:39:10,443
and have low empathy.

528
00:39:11,403 --> 00:39:12,202
But I promise

529
00:39:12,963 --> 00:39:14,483
I'll improve a little every day.

530
00:39:15,562 --> 00:39:16,883
If I can't guess what you're thinking,

531
00:39:17,403 --> 00:39:18,363
I'll just ask you directly.

532
00:39:19,384 --> 00:39:20,360
If there's a misunderstanding,

533
00:39:20,923 --> 00:39:21,883
I'll clarify it.

534
00:39:23,522 --> 00:39:24,323
If I miss you,

535
00:39:24,763 --> 00:39:25,722
I'll come find you.

536
00:39:27,602 --> 00:39:29,363
If I feel something,
I'll share it with you.

537
00:39:31,003 --> 00:39:32,363
I'll be your best friend,

538
00:39:33,363 --> 00:39:33,963
your family,

539
00:39:35,242 --> 00:39:35,803
your partner,

540
00:39:37,483 --> 00:39:38,082
and your teammate.

541
00:39:40,162 --> 00:39:41,042
I'll love you forever,

542
00:39:42,803 --> 00:39:43,483
be by your side

543
00:39:44,763 --> 00:39:46,003
and allow you to be yourself.

544
00:39:52,242 --> 00:39:53,082
I may be

545
00:39:53,963 --> 00:39:55,242
a confused robot,

546
00:39:58,162 --> 00:39:59,202
but I always keep my word.

547
00:40:10,803 --> 00:40:12,082
It's my commitment to you.

548
00:40:20,042 --> 00:40:20,963
You sound

549
00:40:22,403 --> 00:40:24,283
as though you're proposing.

550
00:40:27,722 --> 00:40:28,883
You don't have to say yes now.

551
00:40:30,963 --> 00:40:32,082
I just want you to believe

552
00:40:34,682 --> 00:40:35,843
that I can give you a home.

553
00:40:39,242 --> 00:40:41,122
It's not that I don't want a proposal.

554
00:40:42,522 --> 00:40:43,843
I just feel

555
00:40:44,602 --> 00:40:46,283
that you need
to take it one step at a time.

556
00:40:48,323 --> 00:40:49,722
You haven't even asked me

557
00:40:50,162 --> 00:40:51,642
if I want to be your girlfriend.

558
00:40:56,602 --> 00:40:58,283
Aren't you already my girlfriend?

559
00:40:59,843 --> 00:41:01,202
When did I agree to that?

560
00:41:02,648 --> 00:41:04,104
When we were lying down here last time,

561
00:41:04,363 --> 00:41:05,363
you said you loved me too.

562
00:41:06,803 --> 00:41:08,323
Doesn't that count?

563
00:41:10,162 --> 00:41:11,522
Whether I love you or not,

564
00:41:12,363 --> 00:41:13,803
you can't skip

565
00:41:14,722 --> 00:41:16,082
the necessary steps.

566
00:41:20,562 --> 00:41:21,682
Alright, Ms. Gu Yi.

